     }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":1,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774645729651,"sessionId":"49c2e980-a364-4776-b608-51bf4c3fb234","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":51684,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/49c2e980-a364-4776-b608-51bf4c3fb234.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job asking me to check for active sessions and if none exist, perform autonomous learning about relevant industries for 道简网络 (Daojian Network).\n\nLet me check the sessions_list first to see if there are any active conversations."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vyfowrzbwnvp_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774645730145}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774645733998}}
{"type":"message","id":"a478076a","parentId":"8ca0f873","timestamp":"2026-03-27T21:08:58.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session found is the cron job session itself - this is the current session running. There are no other user conversations in the last 5 minutes. So I should proceed with the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services - industries relevant to 道简网络.","thinkingSignature":"bf827eb5ab52a263f8590e5b49456ba923dc45c42d3659929e44fa3282ecdca2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n当前只有cron任务自身在运行，没有用户活跃对话。执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k6ap9ovcwkzc_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":882,"output":132,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44995,"cost":{"input":0.0002646,"output":0.0001584,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017424299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774645734001}}
{"type":"message","id":"30d7a305","parentId":"a478076a","timestamp":"2026-03-27T21:08:58.893Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k6ap9ovcwkzc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774645738888}}
{"type":"message","id":"b078fb3c","parentId":"30d7a305","timestamp":"2026-03-27T21:09:05.006Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for the latest news on enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services. I'll do multiple searches in parallel to gather information.","thinkingSignature":"6b612233e9f26d0156e3e4dcd369a70d6996653778896ff90b3d01c67c477ddb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p8w68e4mctok_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新动态 政策\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p8w68e4mctok_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p8w68e4mctok_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业发展趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p8w68e4mctok_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1529,"output":239,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45749,"cost":{"input":0.0004587,"output":0.0002868,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00206493}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774645738892}}
